      "metadata": {
        "title": "Lesbian Singles \u2013 Meet & Date",
        "subtitle": "LGBTQ+ Women Dating & Chat",
        "promotional_text": null,
        "description": "Looking to connect with like-minded lesbian and LGBTQ+ women near you?\nLesbian Singles is a friendly space where you can meet, chat, and match with real people in a safe and welcoming community.\n\nStart chatting with amazing women nearby or across the world. Whether you're looking for friendship, love, or just someone who understands you, this app helps you connect naturally and comfortably.\n\nHow it works:\n\nBrowse profiles of lesbian and LGBTQ+ women\n\nTap the heart icon to like someone\n\nIf they like you back, it's a match and you can chat instantly\n\nKey Features:\n\nChat with local lesbian and bi women\n\nFind meaningful matches\n\nShare photos, voice messages, and more\n\nEnjoy a supportive and inclusive space\n\nMeet new people and build real connections\n\nNo pressure, no judgment. Whether you're hoping to meet someone nearby or make new friends around the world, Lesbian Singles gives you the tools to do it.\n\nFree to use with optional upgrades:\nMost features can be unlocked for free by uploading a photo, inviting friends, or engaging with the app. You can also choose to purchase:\n\n100 coins for $1.99\n\n1500 coins for $19.99\n\n3000 coins for $34.99\n\nUpgrade to a Power Account for premium features:\n\n3 months for $29.99\n\n6 months for $41.99\n\n12 months for $59.99\n\nSubscriptions renew automatically unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can manage your subscription in your iTunes account settings.\n\nYour privacy matters.\nYou control your experience and who you interact with. We are committed to creating a respectful space for everyone.\n\nPrivacy Policy and Terms: http://lezsingles.ignite.technology/privacy\n",
